{
  "stem": "1775.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "We just slept under the skies.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And my husband and the other men used to go back in the evening, to get us dry clothes.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "They used to cross the river and go into the ghetto, and get some things.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "In the ghetto, they met another two men-- one man that just came back from Treblinka, and another [? learned ?] man-- [NON-ENGLISH], they called him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they brought those two men to us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we were sitting-- we used to go out in the evening.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We used to go out on the field and dig up potatoes and carrots, and whatever was growing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we used to cook in water.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We used to make a little fire, and at one particular place.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we used to cook our-- whatever we had a chance, we used to cook.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I guess the people realized that we were there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And one day, that was just before Sukkot.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "That [? learned ?] man said, today is Sukkot, and we got to build a sukkah.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he went up to look, to find a place where to build a sukkah, or where probably-- if we would be normal people, we would build a sukkah.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Just then, an idea about a sukkah.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And we went up there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He went first, and the other men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I followed him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "One of the girls from [NON-ENGLISH], Malka her name was, was sitting in that spot, where we were cooking and peeling potatoes.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she was killed, instantly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And her brother was running towards her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "So he caught a bullet in his shoulder.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we all dispersed, again, and ran away.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "At night we came back, again, to the same place, to see who was alive and who wasn't.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Just that girl was dead.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
